 Sharon Van Etten 和 The Attachment Theory 分享大气的新单曲“Trouble” https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-the-attachment-theory-share-atmospheric-new-single-trouble-3829415?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sharon-van-etten-依恋理论分享大气新单身烦恼Tom SkinnerThu, 16 Jan 2025 07:28:10 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3829415 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sahren-Van-Etten-AT@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莎朗·范·埃滕和依恋理论" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sahren-Van-Etten-AT@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sahren-Van-Etten-AT@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sahren-Van-Etten-AT@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sahren-Van-Etten-AT@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sahren-Van-Etten-AT@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sahren-Van-Etten-AT@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这是关于必须与你所爱的持相反观点的人共存”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-the-attachment-theory-share-atmospheric-new-single-trouble-3829415">Sharon Van Etten 和 The Attachment Theory 分享的大气新单曲“Trouble”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sahren-Van-Etten-AT@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莎朗·范·埃滕和依恋理论" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sahren-Van-Etten-AT@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sahren-Van-Etten-AT@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sahren-Van-Etten-AT@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sahren-Van-Etten-AT@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sahren-Van-Etten-AT@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sahren-Van-Etten-AT@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sharon-van-etten">Sharon Van Etten 和 The Attachment Theory</a>分享了一首名为“Trouble”的新单曲 - 请听下面。</p><p>这首大气而低调的歌曲是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-the-attachment-theory-launch-epic-single-afterlife-self-titled-debut-album-uk-european-tour-3805610">该乐队同名专辑</a>的最终预览，该专辑将于 2 月 7 日通过 Jagjaguwar 发行（ <a href="https://sharon-van-etten.lnk.to/and-the-attachment-theory" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>）。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/sharon-van-etten-cover-interview-2022-weve-been-going-about-this-all-wrong-3204585">Sharon Van Etten 采访：“我必须充满希望。我是一名母亲，我想为了我的儿子勇敢”</a></strong></li></ul><p> “‘麻烦’是指必须与你所爱的持有相反观点的人共存，无法根据别人的信仰分享你自己的深层部分和你的叙述，”范·埃滕解释道。</p><p> “爱你的人无法了解你的很大一部分，因为这不是他们想听、也不愿意了解或理解的东西。当你选择爱和尊重别人的需求而不是自己的需求来挽救一段关系时，这是痛苦的时刻。”</p><p> <em>“我不想违背你的意愿失去你的爱/给你一个飞吻并服下一颗药丸/杀人/我不想违背你的意愿失去你的爱/给你一个飞吻并服下一颗药丸/杀死/我不想失去你</em>，”Van Etten 用空灵的声音唱道。</p><p>她在 Devra Hoff 富有感染力的低音线中演绎了自己的​​部分，为 Teeney Lieberson 的华丽而喜怒无常的合成器让路。</p><p>该乐队还分享了在伦敦北部克劳奇恩德的教堂工作室录制的《Trouble》现场表演视频。在这里查看两个版本： </p><p><iframe title="Sharon Van Etten 与依恋理论 - Trouble（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hu3aQKiq-hk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe title="Sharon Van Etten 与依恋理论 - Trouble（伦敦教堂工作室现场直播）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jUiLrV5AC_g?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Trouble》是 Sharon Van Etten &amp; The Attachment Theory 2024 年单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-the-attachment-theory-launch-epic-single-afterlife-self-titled-debut-album-uk-european-tour-3805610">《Afterlife》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-the-attachment-theory-share-trippy-new-single-southern-life-what-it-must-be-like-3818874">《Southern Life (What It Must Be Like)》</a>的后续作品。</p><p>在一系列欧洲演出之后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-the-attachment-theory-launch-epic-single-afterlife-self-titled-debut-album-uk-european-tour-3805610">，乐队将于三月份在英国演出三场头条演出</a>。这些活动将在伦敦皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅、曼彻斯特阿尔伯特音乐厅和格拉斯哥巴罗兰宴会厅举行。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/sharon-van-etten-tickets/artist/1477290?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=xOnTBHWu7xyKRF4SKGSfxVZQUks0%3A9VdGVH-Tg0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里查找剩余的门票</a>。</p><p>北美赛段将于春季举行 - <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此查找门票</a>。八月，Van Etten 等人。将返回英国，在多塞特郡<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/end-of-the-road-2025-line-up-headlined-by-father-john-misty-caribou-self-esteem-sharon-van-etten-the-attachment-theory-3819119">End Of The Road 2025</a>举办的一场重要音乐节表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-announces-new-single-afterlife-coming-next-week-3802766">去年夏天，莎朗·范·埃滕 (Sharon Van Etten) 在伦敦 100 俱乐部举行的低调低调演出</a>中向歌迷介绍了新的“莎朗·范·埃滕与依恋理论” (Sharon Van Etten &amp; The Attachment Theory) 绰号。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sharon Van Etten 与 Nick Cave 合作新专辑《We&#39;ve Been Going About This All Wrong》谈话中" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/emb