a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/live/c3rwqpj70ert" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国广播公司</em></a>报道，联合国还回应称，该协议允许增加向巴勒斯坦人提供援助。</p><p>巴勒斯坦裔模特贝拉·哈迪德 (Bella Hadid) 一直与姐姐吉吉 (Gigi) 一起倡导结束战争，她在 Instagram Stories 上分享了一段巴勒斯坦人庆祝这一协议的片段。 “我的心已经支离破碎”，她写道。 “有很多话要说”。</p><p>说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/macklemore">Macklemore</a>为巴勒斯坦援助发行了单曲《Hind&#39;s Hall》和《Hind&#39;s Hall 2》，他在社交媒体上用一段孩子们听到这一消息的片段分享了他的喜悦之情。 “泪水……停火！！！自由巴勒斯坦”，他写道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DE3CFv1yYnT/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,6